    icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.45 20.45h-3.55v-5.57c0-1.33-.03-3.04-1.85-3.04-1.86 0-2.14 1.45-2.14 2.95v5.66H9.36V9h3.41v1.56h.05c.47-.9 1.63-1.85 3.35-1.85 3.58 0 4.24 2.36 4.24 5.43v6.31zM5.34 7.43a2.06 2.06 0 01-2.06-2.06 2.06 2.06 0 012.06-2.06 2.06 2.06 0 012.06 2.06 2.06 2.06 0 01-2.06 2.06zm1.78 13.02H3.56V9h3.56v11.45z"/></svg>`,
